Drop this into your Vite React app and import wherever you need the logo. It keeps the same animation and is fully responsive via className/props.

tsx
import React from "react";

type Props = {
  className?: string;
  title?: string;
};

const Creative4AILogo: React.FC<Props> = ({ className, title = "Creative 4 AI logo" }) => {
  return (
    <svg
      className={className}
      viewBox="0 0 720 260"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      role="img"
      aria-label={title}
    >
      <defs>
        <radialGradient id="pulseGrad" cx="0" cy="0" r="1" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
          gradientTransform="translate(130 130) rotate(0) scale(110)">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#FFFFFF" stopOpacity="0.85">
            <animate attributeName="stop-opacity" values="0.85;0.55;0.85" dur="6s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </stop>
          <stop offset="55%" stopColor="#5AA7FF">
            <animate attributeName="stop-color" values="#5AA7FF;#8B5CF6;#FF7A59;#5AA7FF" dur="12s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          </stop>
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#111827" stopOpacity="0" />
        </radialGradient>

        <linearGradient id="flowGrad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#5AA7FF" />
          <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#8B5CF6" />
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#FF7A59" />
          <animate attributeName="x1" values="0%;100%;0%" dur="10s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
          <animate attributeName="x2" values="100%;200%;100%" dur="10s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
        </linearGradient>

        <filter id="softShadow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
          <feDropShadow dx="0" dy="6" stdDeviation="12" floodColor="#000000" floodOpacity="0.35" />
        </filter>
      </defs>

      {/* Logomark */}
      <g filter="url(#softShadow)">
        <path
          d="M130,20 A110,110 0 1 0 130,240 A80,80 0 1 1 130,60"
          fill="#0F172A"
        />
      </g>

      <circle cx="130" cy="130" r="95" fill="url(#pulseGrad)" opacity="0.95" />
      <path
        d="M210,110 C190,110 165,110 150,95 C140,85 140,75 140,65 L210,65 Z"
        fill="url(#flowGrad)"
        opacity="0.9"
      />

      {/* Logotype */}
      <g transform="translate(270, 75)">
        <text
          x="0"
          y="0"
          fontFamily="Inter, Poppins, Segoe UI, system-ui, -apple-system, Arial, sans-serif"
          fontSize="64"
          fontWeight="800"
          fill="#0F172A"
          dominantBaseline="hanging"
          letterSpacing="1.5"
        >
          CREATIVE
        </text>
        <text
          x="0"
          y="82"
          fontFamily="Inter, Poppins, Segoe UI, system-ui, -apple-system, Arial, sans-serif"
          fontSize="72"
          fontWeight="800"
          fill="#0F172A"
          letterSpacing="2"
        >
          4 AI
        </text>
        <rect x="2" y="162" width="300" height="10" rx="5" fill="url(#flowGrad)" />
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default Creative4AILogo;

Usage (React):

tsx
import Creative4AILogo from "./Creative4AILogo";

export default function Header() {
  return (
    <header className="flex items-center gap-4 p-4">
      <Creative4AILogo className="w-[360px] h-auto" />
    </header>
  );
}

Notes & tweaks

  • Works on dark or light backgrounds. If you want light-mode text, change fill="#0F172A" to #111827 (dark) or #F9FAFB (light).

  • To slow or speed up the color flow, change dur="10s" on the linearGradient <animate> elements.

  • If you need no animation (e.g., for export), just remove both <animate> tags and the <animate> inside the radial gradient.

✅ Solution 1: Use CSS prefers-color-scheme

You can wrap the SVG inside your React/HTML and apply different filters for light and dark mode using CSS.

Here’s how:

html
<style>
  /* Default (light mode) - softer glow */
  .logo-glow {
    filter: url(#softGlow);
  }

  /* Dark mode - stronger glow for visibility */
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .logo-glow {
      filter: url(#strongGlow);
    }
  }
</style>

<svg width="700" height="200" viewBox="0 0 700 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <!-- Soft Glow for day -->
    <filter id="softGlow" x="-50%" y="-50%" width="200%" height="200%">
      <feGaussianBlur in="SourceGraphic" stdDeviation="6" result="blur"/>
      <feMerge>
        <feMergeNode in="blur"/>
        <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
      </feMerge>
    </filter>

    <!-- Strong Glow for night -->
    <filter id="strongGlow" x="-80%" y="-80%" width="260%" height="260%">
      <feGaussianBlur in="SourceGraphic" stdDeviation="12" result="blur1"/>
      <feGaussianBlur in="SourceGraphic" stdDeviation="20" result="blur2"/>
      <feMerge>
        <feMergeNode in="blur2"/>
        <feMergeNode in="blur1"/>
        <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
      </feMerge>
    </filter>

    <!-- Animated gradient for vinyl highlight -->
    <linearGradient id="animatedGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#4a68ef">
        <animate attributeName="stop-color" values="#4a68ef;#b569f5;#ff7a59;#4a68ef" dur="8s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
      </stop>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#ff7a59">
        <animate attributeName="stop-color" values="#ff7a59;#4a68ef;#b569f5;#ff7a59" dur="8s" repeatCount="indefinite" />
      </stop>
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>

  <!-- Spinning record with glow -->
  <g class="logo-glow" transform="translate(80,100) scale(0.7)">
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="90" fill="none" stroke="#111827" stroke-width="14"/>
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="70" fill="none" stroke="#111827" stroke-width="3"/>
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="60" fill="none" stroke="#111827" stroke-width="2"/>
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="50" fill="none" stroke="#111827" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#111827" stroke-width="1"/>
    <path d="M 50 -50 A 70 70 0 1 0 50 50 L 35 35 A 50 50 0 1 1 35 -35 Z"
          fill="url(#animatedGradient)"/>
    <animateTransform attributeName="transform" attributeType="XML" type="rotate"
                      from="0 0 0" to="360 0 0" dur="6s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
  </g>

  <!-- Text with outline -->
  <text x="200" y="115" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="60" font-weight="bold"
        fill="#ffffff" stroke="#111827" stroke-width="2" class="logo-glow">
    CREATIVE 4 AI
  </text>
</svg>
